{"id":"f93a08a1-04a8-401f-8e59-26d39b440fc0","title":"1494/12/21","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"7ef3de07-d947-4976-85fb-d3c86ed0d523","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"21st December (Sunday). He preached again; and still he did not wish any women to come; he went on discoursing about State matters, and great fear was felt lest the citizen should not agree. Chi la volava lesso e chi arrosto (One wished it boiled and another roast): i.e. everyone had a different opinion, one agreed with the Frate, and another was against him; and if it had not been for him there would have been bloodshed.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"35d25ea4-cda6-4166-aa57-737c742a2b70","type":"codex/time-reference","start":0,"end":21,"value":"ff58fbd8-6395-401d-9ecf-0a4531bbccb5","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c51a5eaa-0729-48bd-9a46-e6e9c05d04d0","type":"style/superscript","start":2,"end":3,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f825ef27-047f-459d-ba6d-c2602bc4edd2","type":"subject","start":24,"end":85,"value":"dcac0c5e-637e-4c41-a5ee-bdb71b3aba3d","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"73f74b12-6f37-4b0d-8c87-6974d6bdd8c9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":24,"end":25,"value":"ac0ccc35-38e8-408c-9be3-055915fcbfe4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"be5d1440-784a-4e9e-94f9-68622f38c6cb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":53,"end":54,"value":"ac0ccc35-38e8-408c-9be3-055915fcbfe4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7acb0f66-f388-4dce-ba71-2a6f062b174a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":88,"end":89,"value":"ac0ccc35-38e8-408c-9be3-055915fcbfe4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"28b957a3-7831-4658-bd37-b0dc0a5ce808","type":"style/italics","start":191,"end":223,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"785d5067-9428-4901-a594-fb3bc88f7ee3","type":"language","start":191,"end":223,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8719c875-9e1b-4a32-97e2-c7f1b5c124f5","type":"style/italics","start":326,"end":330,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"80483145-2eb7-4821-a7bb-d7900a51fc53","type":"language","start":326,"end":330,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9d0031d6-23f6-4041-9bf4-5cb07771f0a5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":326,"end":330,"value":"ac0ccc35-38e8-408c-9be3-055915fcbfe4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1a4ba4c5-60c7-47d5-8750-b09e90e53b86","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":357,"end":359,"value":"ac0ccc35-38e8-408c-9be3-055915fcbfe4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4ede007f-9953-4311-8f3f-76e342dd9f52","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":389,"end":391,"value":"ac0ccc35-38e8-408c-9be3-055915fcbfe4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"89a79d22-5a7c-46cd-974c-673da580a144","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"This evening it was permitted by the Lord, about 2 at night (10 p.m.), in the Via tra\u0027 Ferravecchi,(1) near the Volta della Luna, that my son Benedetto was stabbed in the face, across the cheek, by no means slightly; and we cannot think by whom. We believe it must have been a mistake, as he has never offended anyone or suspected anyone of having a grudge against him: it happened in punishment of our other sins. I freely pardon the aggressor, as I hope that the Lord may pardon me, and I pray God to pardon him and not send him to hell for this.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"3f9d95b7-5c92-4011-a8be-e4c9a987e9e4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":37,"end":40,"value":"a3fed3ec-1814-4027-a2d5-ac598b2fcb6f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ebfb9f32-5de6-478f-a9a7-49dd2f93a5d4","type":"codex/time-reference","start":49,"end":58,"value":"cca02376-79f1-40d1-999e-2dec342b57c4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"797294a8-3ce7-4e72-9833-5fdb240fb09a","type":"codex/time-reference","start":61,"end":67,"value":"fc18f7f8-4f60-45b8-b2a9-c81a6e0742f9","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4a4790cd-48f6-48ae-b203-87ee2dcc61b9","type":"style/italics","start":78,